WEBVTT

00:11:57.368 --> 00:12:00.852
and let me tell you that this
was the first time

00:12:00.852 --> 00:12:05.968
when a campaign was launched by me
or anywhere in the world,

00:12:05.968 --> 00:12:10.041
to educate and sensitize the consumers


00:12:10.041 --> 00:12:14.501
to create a demand
for child-labor-free rugs.

00:12:15.691 --> 00:12:19.083
In Europe and America, 
we have been successful.

00:12:19.083 --> 00:12:23.768
And it has resulted 
in a fall in child labor

00:12:23.768 --> 00:12:27.024
in South Asian countries by 80 percent.

00:12:27.024 --> 00:12:30.406
(Applause)